  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Profitability metrics in Q3 2025 reflect strong operational efficiency, with gross margin at 55.56%, operating margin at 19.61%, and net margin at 17.56%. Net income for the quarter totaled $8,469,000,000, representing a 19.01% YoY growth rate, a significant rebound from the -3.79% decline observed in Q2 2025 when net income was $7,116,000,000. Operating income of $9,456,000,000 in Q3 further underscores improved cost management and revenue quality.",
